-- JPMorgan Sues Lehman, Making Counterclaims Against Defunct Firm
-- B y   L i n d a   S a n d l e r
-- 2010-12-01T22:57:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/jpmorgan-chase-sues-lehman-making-counterclaims-against-bankrupt-firm.html
JPMorgan Chase & Co. sued Lehman
Brothers Holdings Inc., making counterclaims after the defunct
investment bank demanded $8.6 billion plus damages in a May
lawsuit.  JPMorgan was owed $30 billion when Lehman went bankrupt in
September 2008.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Linda Sandler in New York at 
 lsandler@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
 mhytha@bloomberg.net  